Paper: hep-th/0104063

Date: 2001-04-06

Title: The Quantisation of Charges

Authors: David I Olive

Comments: 9 pages, no figures, invited conference talk

The question as to whether the integrality of the spectrum of observedelectric charges is due to a quantum effext has fascinated theoreticalphysicists throughout the last century. It leads to unanswered questions at theheart of quantum field theory and its role as a framework for particle physics.